OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fclear night to come with higher cloud
OL,7,Fmoving into the west of the region.
OL,8,FStaying dry, but gusty winds are
OL,9,Fexpected to continue along coasts and
OL,10,Fover high ground.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother bright and sunny day
OL,13,Fwill follow for all, albeit hazy for
OL,14,Fmany, especially in the west. It will
OL,15,Fremain gusty across the high ground of
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
